Ballantine’s and Boiler Room’s True Music show treated Gengetone fans to their second edition in Kenya. BoilerRoom Show is known for showcasing pioneering artistes changing their local music scenes. The 2020 edition opted to focus on the currently trending Gengetone genre, with performances from Ochungulo Family, DJ Lyta, Boondocks Gang, DJ Kalonje, Rico Gang, DJ Tryce and Femi One. The event, whose location is usually undisclosed and only revealed closer to event day, was held at the International Casino Complex. The next True Music event will be in Bogota, Colombia.